name: YTCracker
description:
'''Bryce Case Jr.''' (born August 23, 1982), otherwise known as '''YTCracker''' (pronounced "''whitey cracker''"), is an American [[rapping|rapper]] from La Mirada, California. His [[stage name]] derives from having formerly been a [[Black hat (computer security)|black hat hacker]]. Case is best known for his contributions to the hacking community along with [[nerdcore]] [[hip hop music|hip hop]] subculture.

During his criminal career, he became known for defacing the webpages of several [[Federal government of the United States|federal]] and municipal government websites in the United States, as well as several in the private industry at the age of 17.
